verbose_text: The SFT immunophenotype (CD34, BCL-2, and/or CD99 expression) by itself is not specific and may be lost during disease progression.6 Some studies have claimed NGFI-A-binding protein 2 (NAB2)-signal transducer and activator of transcription 6 (STAT6) fusion gene, which can be readily detected by STAT6 immunohistochemistry,7, 8, 9 to be hallmarks of SFT.
